    "description": {
      "short": "A content-driven portfolio website with Vite + React frontend and Express + Nodemailer backend.",
      "full": "Saqib Bedar Portfolio is a modern, self-contained portfolio system built with Vite, React, and Tailwind CSS. It features a minimal Express backend for contact emails via Nodemailer, comprehensive caching strategy with 15-minute TTL, in-memory search indexing, and markdown-based blog content. The entire content structure is data-driven through JSON files and asset modules, making customization and reuse straightforward. It includes full documentation, contribution guidelines, and is designed to serve as both a portfolio and a reusable template for other developers."
