    "slug": "online-student-portal",
    "title": "Online Student Portal",

    "description": {
      "short": "Enterprise MERN-based university portal with role-based access and secure session management.",
      "full": "Online Student Portal is a full-scale enterprise-grade university management system built as a freelance project. It implements a hierarchical role-based architecture including Master Admin, Department Admin, Faculty, and Student roles. The system focuses heavily on security and scalability, featuring JWT authentication with HTTP-only cookies, refresh token rotation, concurrent session control, and OTP-based password recovery with rate limiting. The backend follows a modular architecture using controllers and middleware, ensuring maintainability and extensibility."
